cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the ethics of artificial intelligence, which is a subfield of AI. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the decision-making capacities of autonomous systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the values embedded in AI systems, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the practical implementation of ethics in AI, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
